    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《仙之气》是一款带有克苏鲁风格的修仙 RPG。游戏以 “练气” 为核心，玩家将化身练气修士，背负家族复兴使命。通过修炼、探索、集气等方法，不断提修为，寻找线索并获得传说中的仙之气，揭开这个世界隐匿的真相。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196590/extras/cfaf97780f5d58e4963e3992a8bfec9d.avif?t=1756458412\" width=450 height=68 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">欢迎来到仙之气的世界！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">游戏中你将扮演一名突然被任命为一族之长的练气修士</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">一夜之间，天地碎裂，高阶族人离奇失踪</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">只剩下残垣断壁和来历不明的怪物们...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196590/extras/eb0f6b21aeb1e1c0249814a057d1b0bd.avif?t=1756458412\" width=450 height=247 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">你不得已带领剩下的族人前往另一时空下的残破大陆</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">并在此重新建立仙府</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">前往不同的界面寻找各种气息，以补全此界面的法则</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">随着游戏的进行，破碎的大陆会越来越完整</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">直至寻得仙之气</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196590/extras/8351bab66d5f95c304b3cf080ae5deb7.avif?t=1756458412\" width=450 height=247 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196590/extras/aa7dc345027433ca892a0c14f30a40ea.avif?t=1756458412\" width=450 height=68 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>丰富的地块系统</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">本作的修仙世界由地块组合而成，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">是玩家与这个世界互动的载体，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">从青葱草原，再到沙漠戈壁，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">每种地块都有其独特的生态特征，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">给您多样化的修炼体验！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196590/extras/a87fef181aa9af1c83cf2d732bcec773.avif?t=1756458412\" width=416 height=328 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196590/extras/0c8f77c6adc94fc2d51bdc89a0db13e4.avif?t=1756458412\" width=416 height=328 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>集天地之灵气</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">收集天地灵气吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">气息不仅能生万物，还能将其融合，以气炼体</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">据说仙之气就是由某些气息合成出来的哟！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">生成</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196590/extras/b9992a81e85188146d00e9042317c8f1.poster.avif?t=1756458412\" width=472 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196590/extras/b9992a81e85188146d00e9042317c8f1.webm?t=1756458412\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196590/extras/b9992a81e85188146d00e9042317c8f1.mp4?t=1756458412\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">反应</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196590/extras/00c91f4954ac211372bc5a2c0cc6f7e5.poster.avif?t=1756458412\" width=476 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196590/extras/00c91f4954ac211372bc5a2c0cc6f7e5.webm?t=1756458412\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196590/extras/00c91f4954ac211372bc5a2c0cc6f7e5.mp4?t=1756458412\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\">合成</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196590/extras/66c6df50df4107ab3730167da51163d4.poster.avif?t=1756458412\" width=474 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196590/extras/66c6df50df4107ab3730167da51163d4.webm?t=1756458412\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196590/extras/66c6df50df4107ab3730167da51163d4.mp4?t=1756458412\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>功法与造物</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196590/extras/c78cd62fb37279ce8c485054148966c8.avif?t=1756458412\" width=450 height=263 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">参悟！学习！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">分析收集的气息之奥义并内化于心</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">从内功修炼到外功绝技</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">融合所学，开创属于你的独门流派吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196590/extras/0fe4f250b841d21249a179cec0cb36bc.avif?t=1756458412\" width=450 height=257 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">收集！炼造！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">在探索、战斗中灵活利用造物</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">让您的飞升之路更加顺利！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>战斗与探索</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196590/extras/5dda554a676359d08ab957558cac6d14.avif?t=1756458412\" width=450 height=257 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">探索途中我们会遇到各种危险的怪物</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">在回合制的战斗中，操控心法和造物神器击败怪物 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">获得各种奖励吧！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196590/extras/b6ac8a29641679ed5ed5dfa4f08da51e.avif?t=1756458412\" width=450 height=263 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">在探索途中，也会遭遇随机事件的发生， <br>每一次的决策都可能会影响你的仙途走向。 <br>探索副本，收集线索，探寻族人失踪的真相。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>建设你的家族</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3196590/extras/da5f77bbac3810a0d79fab6ade348913.avif?t=1756458412\" width=450 height=491 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">建设仙府与造物设施，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">从随机事件、修士派遣等途径， </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">获取家族培养资源，努力让自己的宗门壮大起来吧。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">随着剧情的发展，族人的结局会因为你的选择产生改变...</p>",
